#. description
#: /opt/splunk/etc/apps/uberAgent_ESA/default/data/ui/views/security_score.xml:11
msgid ""
"The Security Score dashboard monitors the organization's security status by "
"combining the key data sources Security & Compliance Inventory and Threat "
"Detection Engine. It presents a comprehensive overview of the security score "
"on a scale from zero to ten. The higher the score, the better your security "
"level. Overall and category scores are calculated daily and compared to the "
"past seven days, while test and tag analysis utilizes data from the 24 "
"previous hours. Click on a value of interest to get a drilldown. SCI events "
"are evaluated periodically every 30 minutes. To manually trigger the "
"evaluation search, click the 'Refresh Now' button located at the bottom of "
"the dashboard."
msgstr ""

#: /opt/splunk/etc/apps/uberAgent_ESA/default/app.conf:21
msgid ""
"This app contains the dashboards for uberAgent ESA and should be installed "
"on the search head(s). uberAgent ESA is an endpoint security analytics app "
"based on uberAgent."
msgstr ""

